  "content": "<p data-pid=\"Hpmgfh2P\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/35235203\" class=\"internal\">返回目录</a></p><hr/><p data-pid=\"2vmQlpA-\">首先我们先找一份材料，可以是别人归纳的高考成语题常考成语，或者是找一份语文成语题练习，刷它一遍，把自己不会的成语都录到「Anki」中。</p><p data-pid=\"9AH8zuKy\">材料来源：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26345610\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9e7c823538a0a096578f10a1287bb369_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1200\" data-image-height=\"800\" class=\"internal\">那就离开吧：正确使用词语(包括熟语)</a><p data-pid=\"piISREIY\">预览图</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"small\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b123e4658401ae813dd6bb82d24cd7a1_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1280\" data-rawheight=\"2276\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1280\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b123e4658401ae813dd6bb82d24cd7a1_r.jpg\" data-original-token=\"v2-b123e4658401ae813dd6bb82d24cd7a1\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bb2296c198ba1a82bce1c6d23d782e31_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"786\" data-rawheight=\"642\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"786\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-bb2296c198ba1a82bce1c6d23d782e31_r.jpg\" data-original-token=\"v2-f1f740701be0e8e6e399a38d24bb26a0\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"VGL98jyK\">目前有 835 张，背了之后全国卷语文的成语6选3再也不用怕了！</p><p data-pid=\"SjVXtm5Z\">这里先分享一下我整理的</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//ankiweb.net/shared/info/1388324858\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">【高考╳Anki】语文成语 - AnkiWeb</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//pan.baidu.com/s/17d70DIX3tBYFadKIJpF7Xg\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">高考成语牌组-百度云备用</a><blockquote data-pid=\"6gqsDxbG\"><i>赠人一赞，手有余香。</i></blockquote><hr/><p data-pid=\"5lp8UmQL\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/35235203\" class=\"internal\">返回目录</a></p>",
